Titolo: N.O.V.A. 3

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: N.O.V.A. 3 (Near Orbit Vanguard Alliance 3) is Gameloft's third installment of the N.O.V.A. series for iOS, BlackBerry 10 and Android devices, with planned releases for the BlackBerry PlayBook and Windows Phone 8 devices. The game was released on the App Store on May 10, 2012. N.O.V.A. 3 is a science fiction action-adventure first-person shooter video game. Gameloft launched a free-to-play edition of N.O.V.A. 3 which is known as N.O.V.A. 3: Freedom Edition. It features Gameloft's multiplayer service Gameloft Live.

